# sbt / sbt-BSP JVM options (project root `.jvmopts`)
# Managed by stl-ide-toolbox Metals reset — heap capped at 8G.
# Local only — keep in .gitignore; do not commit.
# UnlockExperimentalVMOptions required when the JDK still marks ZGC experimental (e.g. JDK 11).
-Xms100m
-Xmx8G
-Xss4m
-XX:+UnlockExperimentalVMOptions
-XX:+UseZGC
